UINT64 _EFI_SIMPLE_FILE_SYSTEM_PROTOCOL::Revision

The version of the EFI_SIMPLE_FILE_SYSTEM_PROTOCOL. The version specified by this specification is 0x00010000. All future revisions must be backwards compatible.
